msgstr ""
"This `PDF-Dokument <../_static/files/adafruit-gfx-graphics-library.pdf>`_ "
"contains the basic commands of the Adafruit GFX library. You can also access"
" the complete functionality of the library online here `Klassen Referenz`_."

#: ../../programming/pages.rst:159 088a32007b174df997a1dd5e69379d02
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
